03:28.833 --> 03:29.833
<i>Did it open?</i>

03:37.383 --> 03:39.143
<i>- </i> Detective?
<i>- Yeah. Yes.</i>

03:39.886 --> 03:41.721
<i>We have seven more of her.</i>

03:41.804 --> 03:43.932
<i>The others are harder to look at.</i>

03:46.684 --> 03:48.895
I'll send them along,
so you have everything.

03:59.739 --> 04:01.616
Yeah... okay.

04:03.743 --> 04:04.869
