as a new rape charge.

04:40.280 --> 04:41.280
Oh, I can do that.

04:41.823 --> 04:43.449
Oh, look who's landed.

04:49.038 --> 04:50.164
Detective Parker?

04:50.665 --> 04:51.541
Yes, hi.

04:51.624 --> 04:54.085
Grace Rasmussen.
Nice of you to come all this way.

04:54.168 --> 04:55.168
We're in here.

05:08.266 --> 05:09.767
