to give you to bury this.

23:49.970 --> 23:51.054
Tell them I'll take it.

23:51.805 --> 23:54.724
No, look, we can do much better.

23:54.808 --> 23:56.101
I... I don't need better.

23:56.852 --> 23:59.229
A hundred and fifty thousand dollars
is a lot of money.

23:59.479 --> 24:02.039
